{"type":null,"faqId":10977,"title":"荣耀3C （H30-T10&H30-U10）  是否支持3D加速？","answer":"<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">支持。在主屏幕，点击<b>设置</b></span><span> &gt; </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">开发人员选项</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，勾选“<b>强制进行</b></span><b><span>GPU</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">渲染</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">”即可开启。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">开启</span><span>3D</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">加速可以使游戏画面更流畅，但会消耗更大的内存；玩游戏时，消耗更大的内存一般是没有影响的，但如果这时手机运行了很多应用，可能会引起手机变慢。</span> \n</p>","faqTypeId":143,"faqType":"系统功能与设置","useful":0,"unUseful":3,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"1739","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-System-Settings","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1397792147000,"seriesProductName":"H30-T10,H30-U10","visitedTimes":347,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":3,"times":1,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"1","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"荣耀3C （H30-T10&H30-U10）","avgScore":3.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}